00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:40.920
for the trouble.

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:43.880
It's all because

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:46.240
you want your children to succeed.

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:48.760
Zelan is really talented.

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:51.080
Given how she recognized the herbs,

00:12:51.440 --> 00:12:52.280
she's probably

00:12:52.440 --> 00:12:53.880
better than us.

00:12:54.380 --> 00:12:57.640
We must not waste her talent.

00:12:58.080 --> 00:12:58.930
Lord Wu,

00:12:59.000 --> 00:12:59.840
don't worry.

00:13:00.160 --> 00:13:01.920
I'll send her to
the Imperial Medical Bureau

00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:04.080
as a medical attendant
on behalf of our family

00:13:04.400 --> 00:13:06.480
so she can learn from you

00:13:06.880 --> 00:13:07.720
and gain experience.

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:10.960
Zelan,

00:13:11.120 --> 00:13:12.160
the physician's robe carries

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:13.360
the weight of life and death.

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:14.880
Once you're ready,

00:13:15.120 --> 00:13:17.840
we'll be glad to have you as one of us.

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:20.040
Lord Wu,

00:13:20.520 --> 00:13:22.840
I've been determined to become
a physician since childhood.

00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:24.640
My biggest dream

00:13:25.000 --> 00:13:26.640
is to save lives
and relieve people's pain.

00:13:27.200 --> 00:13:28.720
I've been ready for a long time,

00:13:28.960 --> 00:13:31.040
and I will be worthy of
my patients' trust.

00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:35.000
Zelan,

00:13:35.520 --> 00:13:37.040
I'll be waiting for you.

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:38.840
Deal.

00:13:45.540 --> 00:13:51.420
(Tablet of the Beloved Mother, Lady Liu)

00:13:56.760 --> 00:13:57.600
Mom,

00:13:58.320 --> 00:14:00.280
I have good news to tell you.

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:03.360
I'm going to be a medical attendant.

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:06.500
(Tablet of the Beloved Mother, Lady Liu)
These years,

00:14:06.640 --> 00:14:08.840
I've endured all the hardships

00:14:09.640 --> 00:14:11.440
just for this moment.

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:15.080
- Zhang Yueyao was afraid
- Miss Zelan,

00:14:15.080 --> 00:14:17.000
- I'd overshadow Rong Zeyan.
- your favorite pastries.

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:19.640
For the future of her daughter,

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:21.600
she even poisoned me.

00:14:21.920 --> 00:14:22.760
It's good!

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:24.400
To survive,

00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:26.160
I pretended to swallow

00:14:26.160 --> 00:14:28.320
the poisoned food sent by her maid.

00:14:28.720 --> 00:14:29.600
After Tao left,

00:14:30.160 --> 00:14:31.320
I forced myself to vomit

00:14:31.640 --> 00:14:32.920
and saved my sense of taste.

00:14:33.280 --> 00:14:35.920
After Tao completed the mission,

00:14:36.640 --> 00:14:37.680
find an opportunity

00:14:38.280 --> 00:14:39.280
to finish her.

00:14:40.120 --> 00:14:42.480
Only dead bodies don't speak.

00:14:43.080 --> 00:14:46.120
When I found out
she wanted to shut Tao's mouth for good,

00:14:46.640 --> 00:14:48.520
- I realized I had to protect Tao
- Try this.

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:51.320
so that I could turn the tables one day.

00:14:51.760 --> 00:14:53.920
So, I ate the spoiled pastries

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:55.440
right where my aunt would pass by

00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:57.600
- and got Tao sold to another family
- Guards!

00:14:57.960 --> 00:14:59.680
- before Zhang Yueyao could kill her.
- Sold her!

00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:01.520
After Tao was sold,

00:15:02.080 --> 00:15:03.520
I spent a long time searching for her

00:15:03.520 --> 00:15:04.640
and bought her freedom

00:15:05.800 --> 00:15:07.720
so that one day,

00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:09.880
I could testify against Zhang Yueyao.

00:15:10.060 --> 00:15:11.860
(Tablet of the Beloved Mother, Lady Liu)

00:15:12.720 --> 00:15:13.560
Mom,

00:15:14.520 --> 00:15:15.840
now you're watching me from heaven.

00:15:17.040 --> 00:15:18.080
You'll see

00:15:18.480 --> 00:15:20.760
how I will prove your innocence
and clear your name

00:15:21.240 --> 00:15:22.680
after going to the palace.

00:15:24.480 --> 00:15:25.600
For those

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:27.480
who stood by and watched you die,

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:32.440
I will make every one of them
pay the price!